Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located approximately 20km from the Melbourne CBD, the site is located in the very tightly held industrial precinct of Clayton South where it enjoys good access to major roads, public transport, amenity and surrounding residential housing. The property itself is located at the end of Osborne Avenue which is accessed directly off Clayton Road. This provides easy access to Princes Highway to the north and the Dingley Bypass to the south, linking the Melbourne CBD and the south eastern industrial precincts.

Property Features Include:
- Recently undergone major refurbishment works to the warehouse and office
- 607sqm* single level corporate office
- 2,534sqm* warehouse with 4 x 10T cranes.
- Total area 3141sqm*
- 7 motorised container height roller doors
- Internal clearance of up to 9.6m*
- 400amp* power supply with the ability to upgrade further 
- Ability to extend the warehouse by a further 1,100sqm*
- Covered wash bay with triple interceptor
- Substantial hardstand/ truck marshalling areas.
- Industrial 1 Zoning

*denotes approx.    
For more information please contact Josh, Stephen or Sasan
